Gilmário Pinto Vemba (a mụrụ na 19 June 1985), nke a ma ama dịka Gilmário Vemba, bụ onye Angola na-eme ihe nkiri na onye na-eme ọchị. A maara ya nke ọma maka ọrụ ya na ihe nkiri telivishọn O Bar do Gilmário, After Party na Fora de Série
Ọ bụbu onye otu egwuregwu "os Tuneza".
A mụrụ ya n'abalị 19 ọnwa Julaị afọ 1985 na Luanda, Angola. Ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ na International Relations and Political Analysis
Ọ lụrụ di ma bụrụ nna ụmụ nwanyị atọ na otu nwa nwoke.
N'afọ 2003, Vemba na Daniel Vilola, Orlando Rodrigues, Cesalty Paulo na José Chieta guzobere otu ihe ọchị os Tuneza
Ọ gara n'ihu n'òtù ahụ ruo ihe karịrị afọ iri na ise, ruo mgbe ọ hapụrụ otu ahụ n'afọ 2020. N'afọ 2019, o gosipụtara ihe ngosi na-atọ ọchị na Portugal n'aha "Imortal".

N'afọ 2021, o mere ihe nkiri izizi ya na A Dívida (The Debt) nke Anacleto de Abreu duziri. Emere ihe nkiri ahụ na 26th February 2021 na Cinemax, na Luanda. N'ọnwa Julaị afọ 2021, ọ bịanyere aka na ihe ngosi ọhụrụ nke TVI bụ O Amor Acontece
Kemgbe afọ 2022, ọ bụ otu n'ime ndị na-asọmpi na-adịgide adịgide nke mbipụta Portuguese nke "Taskmaster" (RTP1).
